item.title: By: Virginia Reeves
item.dc:creator: Virginia Reeves
item.description: Sabrina - my favorite part is the analogy of replacing the unwanted item (thought, belief, or emotion) with something beautiful you don't want to junk up. I've been working (again) on both physical and internal clutter. It can be sticky but it's worth ridding yourself of the junk and gunk.
